prompts.frontCover:
Minimalist greeting card front, 2D flat illustration. A clean, off-white background. Centered, a humorous cartoon scene featuring the two people from the reference photo.

Lao Lao (person on left) is illustrated with a huge, joyful smile, effortlessly lifting Jordan (person on right) over her shoulder in a fireman's carry. Jordan has a comically surprised and slightly bewildered expression on his face, arms flailing slightly. They are both wearing simplified versions of their outfits from the photo: Lao Lao in a blue sweatshirt and dark pants, and Jordan in a tan hoodie and dark pants.

Directly below the characters, in a beautiful, readable, dark grey handwritten cursive script, the text reads: "Happy Birthday to my strong Lao Lao".

The illustration style is simple, using clean lines, solid colors, and minimal shading to maintain a modern, minimalist aesthetic. No background elements, just the characters and text.
